graph LR
    DSPO[Data Science Pipelines<br/>Operator]

    %% External Dependencies (Required/Conditional)
    DSPO -->|container platform| K8s[Kubernetes/OpenShift 4.11+]
    DSPO -->|workflow engine<br/>v2 deployments| Argo[Argo Workflows]
    DSPO -->|workflow engine<br/>v1 deployments| Tekton[OpenShift Pipelines<br/>Tekton 1.8+]
    DSPO -->|TLS certificates| CertMgr[cert-manager /<br/>Service CA]
    DSPO -.->|production database<br/>optional| ExtDB[External Database<br/>MariaDB/MySQL 10.3+]
    DSPO -.->|production storage<br/>optional| ExtS3[External S3<br/>AWS/Ceph/Minio]
    DSPO -->|authentication| OAuth[OpenShift OAuth<br/>Provider]

    %% Internal ODH Dependencies
    DSPO -->|deployed by| ODHOp[opendatahub-operator]
    Dashboard[ODH Dashboard] -->|UI integration<br/>API calls| DSPO
    Elyra[Elyra] -->|pipeline authoring<br/>SDK client| DSPO

    %% Integration Points
    DSPO -->|metrics scraping| Prometheus[Prometheus]
    DSPO -->|resource mgmt<br/>CR watches| K8sAPI[Kubernetes API<br/>6443/TCP]
    DSPO -.->|service mesh<br/>optional| ServiceMesh[Service Mesh<br/>mTLS]

    %% Runtime Dependencies (Created by DSPO)
    subgraph "Per-Instance Components (Created by DSPO)"
        MariaDB[MariaDB<br/>dev/test]
        Minio[Minio<br/>dev/test]
    end

    DSPO -->|deploys| MariaDB
    DSPO -->|deploys| Minio

    %% Styling
    style DSPO fill:#4a90e2,stroke:#333,stroke-width:4px,color:#fff

    %% External dependencies
    style K8s fill:#999,stroke:#333,color:#fff
    style Argo fill:#999,stroke:#333,color:#fff
    style Tekton fill:#999,stroke:#333,color:#fff
    style CertMgr fill:#999,stroke:#333,color:#fff
    style OAuth fill:#999,stroke:#333,color:#fff
    style ExtDB fill:#e8e8e8,stroke:#333
    style ExtS3 fill:#e8e8e8,stroke:#333
    style K8sAPI fill:#999,stroke:#333,color:#fff
    style Prometheus fill:#999,stroke:#333,color:#fff
    style ServiceMesh fill:#e8e8e8,stroke:#333

    %% Internal ODH
    style ODHOp fill:#7ed321,stroke:#333
    style Dashboard fill:#7ed321,stroke:#333
    style Elyra fill:#7ed321,stroke:#333

    %% Deployed components
    style MariaDB fill:#bd10e0,stroke:#333,color:#fff
    style Minio fill:#bd10e0,stroke:#333,color:#fff
